text: For 39 minutes and 59 seconds of game time, Cal did not lead USF and Makale Foreman didn't make a shot. Then Foreman buried a buzzer-beating 3-pointer from the left side, and the Bears exulted over their 72-70 victory over the Dons. https://t.co/dOAYun1SUb
